      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study (coarse, medium, fine) performed on the pedicle screw construct. QoI change between medium and fine mesh was 1.1% for stiffness and 1.4% for yield force. Richardson extrapolation applied; GCI < 2% for all QoIs. Required level 2 achieved."
