      "rationale": "Nonlinear solver residuals converged to below 1e-6 force norm for all load steps. Energy balance error < 0.1%. Default sparse direct solver used; no iterative solver divergence observed. Required level 1 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
