      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm displacement) directly map to regulatory submission requirements for ASTM F1717 performance characterization.",
      "rationale": "The three QoIs are explicitly required by ASTM F1717 and FDA guidance for pedicle screw system submissions. Each QoI is directly interpretable in terms of clinical performance (construct rigidity, onset of permanent deformation, post-yield load capacity). Required level 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
