    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/nagaraja-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 V&V 40 factors and determined that the FEA modeling framework demonstrates sufficient credibility for the stated COU. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) was reviewed and deemed acceptable given the strong quantitative agreement across all QoIs, the cross-laboratory experimental validation, and the conservative nature of the single test condition relative to in vivo loading. Overall assurance level assessed as Medium, consistent with model risk level 3 and the observed factor profile.",
